# 🎮 Simon Says Memory Game (BARR-C Compliant)

A Simon Says memory game developed with **Arduino UNO** following the **BARR-C Embedded C Coding Standard**.

This project demonstrates:

- 🟢 State Machine Programming
- 🟢 Modular Embedded Software Design
- 🟢 Arduino Programming
- 🟢 4×4 Matrix Keypad
- 🟢 I2C LCD Display
- 🟢 LED Sequence Memory Logic
- 🟢 Passive Buzzer Feedback
- 🟢 Wokwi Simulation
- 🟢 Professional Documentation

