# 🧰 Hardware Used

- Arduino UNO
- 16×2 I2C LCD
- 4×4 Matrix Keypad
- 4 LEDs
- Passive Buzzer
- Push Button
- Breadboard
- 330Ω Resistors
- Jumper Wires

---

# 💻 Software Used

- PlatformIO
- VS Code
- Wokwi Simulator
- Git
- GitHub

---

# 🚀 Future Improvements

- Score display
- High score memory (EEPROM)
- Difficulty selection
- Sound effects
- RGB LEDs
- OLED Display
- FreeRTOS Version

